(**
 3. Extensivity
 *)
Section DisjointCoproducts.
  Context (C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ : bicat_of_univ_cats_with_biinitial_bincoprod).

  Notation "‚àÅ" := bicat_of_univ_cats_with_biinitial_bincoprod.

  Let R := @biinitial_comma_cone
             ‚àÅ
             C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ
             (pr1 (bincoprod_of ‚àÅ C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ))
             (inl_functor _ _)
             (inr_functor _ _).

  Section OneCell.
    Context (Q : @comma_cone

Section UniversalCoproducts.
  Notation "‚àÅ" := bicat_of_univ_cats_with_biinitial_bincoprod.

  Context {C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ Z : ‚àÅ}
          (F : Z --> pr1 (bincoprod_of ‚àÅ C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ)).

  Let Œπ‚ÇÅ : C‚ÇÅ --> pr1 (bincoprod_of ‚àÅ C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ)
    := inl_functor (pr1 C‚ÇÅ) (pr1 C‚ÇÇ).
  Let Œπ‚ÇÇ : C‚ÇÇ --> pr1 (bincoprod_of ‚àÅ C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ)
    := inr_functor (pr1 C‚ÇÅ) (pr1 C‚ÇÇ).

  Let Œ∫‚ÇÅ : bicat_of_univ_cats ‚ü¶ univalent_iso_comma Œπ‚ÇÅ F , Z ‚üß
    := iso_comma_pr2 _ _.
  Let Œ∫‚ÇÇ : bicat_of_univ_cats ‚ü¶ univalent_iso_comma Œπ‚ÇÇ F , Z ‚üß
    := iso_comma_pr2 _ _.

  Section UniversalCoproductsOne.
    Context (W : @bincoprod_cocone
                   bicat_of_univ_cats
                   (univalent_iso_comma Œπ‚ÇÅ F)
                   (univalent_iso_comma Œπ‚ÇÇ F)).

        apply (homset_property (pr111 (bincoprod_of ‚àÅ C‚ÇÅ C‚ÇÇ)) (inr y‚ÇÅ)).

        apply id_right.
